Package: raspkali-widget
Version: 1.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Depends: python3, python3-psutil, python3-requests, python3-pyqt5, lm-sensors
Maintainer: ManChoi Gomez <manchoig@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/manchoig/raspkali-widget
Description: Floating system monitor widget for Raspberry Pi
 A frameless floating widget that displays real-time system metrics
 including CPU temperature, RAM, disk usage, network interfaces,
 open ports, and service status. Configurable via config.ini with
 automatic log management and configurable retention policy.